blog.name: askyourownhero
blog.title: You're The Hero!
blog.description: Welcome, hero! You're newly transferred into the prestigious hero class; 1-A after a particularly successful sports festival, and you're ready to try your best! . . . . . . . (Please read about link before sending asks!)

title: Your Journey Begins
body:
So you wish to exist?

As a young teenager enrolled in UA? A hero-in-training bustling with youthful-hope and energy?

Well that does sound fun.

But to exist, we might need something a bit more physical, rather than just a loose concept.

So the age-old question, and the first one too;

What is your gender?

  • Born Female
  • Born Male
  • Trans Female
  • Trans Male
  • Genderfluid
  • Agender
  • Other(Please specify! <3)

This is the first question towards creating the muse of this askblog! This question isn’t directed at specifically you, but the the character you all will be creating together.

You will be creating the very hero-in-training and the focus of this askblog, they will participate in class 1-A at UA, and interact with many of the cannon characters from BNHA.

The time it will be set in is directly after the sports festival, expect the canon events of the show/manga to eventually happen in the askblog as well. Whether you all(the askers) decide that muse participates in the canon events or not depends.

For most future decisions, you all will be expected to send in asks with what you want the muse to do, but currently for creating the muse first, I will depend on people voting in a poll. So it may be a bit more organised. Though I plan for using a poll to be only a one-off for the character creation portion of this askblog.

Vote the muse’s gender in the poll, please!

Now decide!
